# Privacy Policy

**Last updated: March 2024**

## 1. Introduction

Welcome to **Quote Moment**. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data when you use our app and tell you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.

## 2. Data We Collect

We collect the following types of data:

- Email address (for account creation and authentication)  
- Nickname (for personalization)  
- User-generated quotes and content  
- App usage statistics and preferences  
- Theme preferences (light/dark mode)  
- Device type, operating system version, and app version (for diagnostic purposes)
- Language and region settings (for localization)


## 3. How We Use Your Data

We use your data to:

- Provide and maintain our app  
- Personalize your experience  
- Improve our services  
- Communicate with you about updates and changes  
- Ensure app security and prevent fraud  
- Analyze usage patterns to enhance app performance and user experience


## 4. Data Storage and Security

- Your data is stored securely using **Firebase Authentication** and **Firestore**  
- We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal data  
- Your quotes and content are stored in a secure database  
- We use industry-standard encryption for data transmission  
- We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you services


## 5. Your Rights

You have the right to:

- Access your personal data  
- Correct inaccurate data  
- Request deletion of your data  
- Object to processing of your data  
- Export your quotes and content  

## 6. Third-Party Services

We use the following third-party services:

- **Firebase** (Authentication and Database)  
- **Apple Sign In**  
- **Google Analytics** (for app improvement)  
All third-party services we use comply with GDPR and CCPA regulations, where applicable.


## 7. Children's Privacy

Our app is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
If we become aware that we have collected personal data from a child under 13 without verified parental consent, we will take steps to delete that information.


## 8. Changes to This Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.

## 9. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

- **Email:** yevheniiyurievdev@gmail.com
- **Through the app's support section**

## 10. Data Deletion Requests

You can request deletion of your account and personal data at any time by:

- Emailing us at: yevheniiyurievdev@gmail.com
- Using the "Delete Account" feature in the app (if available)

We aim to process all deletion requests within 30 days.
We do not sell your personal data to third parties.

Terms of Use (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/


---

This Privacy Policy is effective as of **March 2024** and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page.
